    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %h1 You have been invited to a league on CTFLeague!
    %p
      If you are already a member of CTFLeague, follow the link below to accept the invitation. You'll need to enter your League Key, which is <strong>#{@league_key}</strong>.
    %p
      If you aren't yet a member, please sign up for CTFLeague, then follow the link below.
    %p
      To log in to the site, just follow this link: <a href="
      = league_url(@league_id)
      ">
      = league_url(@league_id)
      </a>
